TITLE: Episode 96 - Enter the Soundman (featuring Dent)
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined yet again by the best guy to ever grace the bird app, Dent a.k.a @dentintheworld. Owner of ZenPro Audio and patron and benefactor of many of the best creators around, Dent returns to shoot the proverbial shit and have a great time with good friends. Join us in this very exciting love fest.
